Usage:

  steroids <command> [arguments]

Commands:

  create APP_PATH

    Creates a new application from default template.

  make

    Runs grunt tasks and creates files in dist.

  package

    Packages application for build.

  build

    Starts server and shows a QR-code for AppGyver Scanner.

  serve

    Starts a web server that serves files from dist directory.

  debug

    Starts Weinre debugger and waits for connections.

  simulator

    Launches iOS Simulator, requires xCode.
